{"tid":883732,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［Marvel] Winter Solider將伙拍Falcon開拍限定劇為迪士尼串流服務打頭陣","createTime":"2018-10-31T05:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T14:00:02.000Z","uid":197222,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18c02d95794aa0904003f95c89d7556626104333","tid":883732,"uid":197222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/130050_ec35b484231cac9203549ee91dfebaf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F130050_ec35b484231cac9203549ee91dfebaf7.png&h=a2fe9202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在《美國隊長3：英雄內戰》裡，獵鷹（Falcon）與巴奇（Bucky）這對歡喜冤家之間有不少令人印象深刻的逗趣互動，因戲結緣的演員安東尼˙麥基（Anthony Mackie）與賽巴斯汀˙史坦（Sebastian Stan）在戲外也是一對哥倆好，時常在訪談裡一起耍寶、搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n由於兩人在幕前幕後的表現，許多粉絲不免期待能在本系列作品裡看到更多相關的戲份，就連演員本人都曾打趣地表示他們已經向Marvel進行了提案，希望能製作一部以巴奇與獵鷹為主角的搭檔電影。<br />\n<br />\n根據最新的消息，這個構想或許將有機會以不同的方式實現。<br />\n<br />\nVariety今天稍早在一篇獨家報導中指出：為了替籌備中的線上串流影音平台充實獨家內容，迪士尼目前正在規劃一部以獵鷹與巴奇為主角的影集，並已邀請曾參與過《嘻哈世家》（Empire）製作的麥爾坎˙史貝爾曼（Malcolm Spellman）為其撰寫劇本。<br />\n<br />\n先前曾有消息指出，緋紅女巫（Scarlet Witch）與洛基（Loki）等其他同屬Marvel電影世界觀的角色也將會是迪士尼影音串流平台的主力之一，但獵鷹與巴奇的影集則是目前最先傳出編劇人選消息的計畫。<br />\n<br />\n對於Variety今天的報導，Marvel與迪士尼方面則不願發表任何評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/falcon-winter-soldier-limited-series-marvel-1203015438/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2018%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Ffalcon-winter-soldier-limited-series-marvel-1203015438%2F&d=HetuhokjshoFeYmKQ5or8TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6db49ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/falcon-winter-soldier-limited-series-marvel-1203015438/</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: Marvel電影世界觀百科"},{"pid":"670da7e5420d0fbf15fb6f9b963fc6c4c5a24522","tid":883732,"uid":197222,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/131109_79863ff7e7c1ecba70b416c68cfdca71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F131109_79863ff7e7c1ecba70b416c68cfdca71.png&h=f06fd298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連同紅女巫同Loki暫定已經有三套MCU限定劇幫迪迪尼黎緊個streaming service撐場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c24375b3fafde840cb6abee2a9147e5e2207bd","tid":883732,"uid":70150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:23:06.000Z","msg":"我同做CA 同WS 既地下情呀"},{"pid":"7fba134886edd0cb85cc39f1e4485c28612aa80b","tid":883732,"uid":70150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想睇CA 同WS 既地下情呀</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c88c39720b854196e3423d2f66a9c9c38ea90295","tid":883732,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"聽收皮"},{"pid":"71a4c7084f4a02c771c167830b6d7b5a24cc5b18","tid":883732,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"Limited Series限定劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c283da7fd4aadf09d9489fe9b27dff1d3f5bee2","tid":883732,"uid":44412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fba134886edd0cb85cc39f1e4485c28612aa80b","tid":883732,"uid":70150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想睇CA 同WS 既地下情呀</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"bucky?"},{"pid":"e24dfcc4e47409aca184f4bcb0002f5156